'''亚铬酸铜'''是一种[[无机化合物|无机化合物]]，化学式Cu<sub>2</sub>Cr<sub>2</sub>O<sub>5</sub>。它是一种黑色固体，为[[有机合成|有机合成]]中的催化剂。<ref>Cladingboel, D. E. "Copper Chromite" in Encyclopedia of Reagents for Organic Synthesis 2001 John Wiley & Sons. {{doi|10.1002/047084289X.rc221}}</ref>

==历史==
亚铬酸铜于1908年首次被描述。<ref>{{cite journal|doi= 10.1002/zaac.19120760103|title= Chromite aus basischen Chromaten|journal= Zeitschrift für Anorganische Chemie|volume= 76|pages= 30–38|year= 1912|last1= Gröger|first1= Max|url= https://zenodo.org/record/1428128|access-date= 2021-11-02|archive-date= 2021-11-05|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20211105065810/https://zenodo.org/record/1428128|dead-url= no}}</ref>这种催化剂由{{le|Homer Burton Adkins}}和Wilbur Arthur Lazier在北美开发，部分基于[[二战|二战]]之后对[[德国|德国]]化学家与[[费托合成|费托合成]]相关的审问。<ref name=Lazier>{{cite journal|last1=Adkins|first1=Homer|last2=Burgoyne|first2=Edward|last3=Schneider|first3=Henry|title=The Copper—Chromium Oxide Catalyst for Hydrogenation|journal=Journal of the American Chemical Society|date=1950|volume=72|issue=6|pages=2626–2629|doi=10.1021/ja01162a079}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.fischer-tropsch.org/primary_documents/gvt_reports/USNAVY/tech_rpt_248_45/tech_rpt_248_45_sec6.htm |title=Fischer–Tropsch Archive |access-date=2021-11-02 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924013657/http://www.fischer-tropsch.org/primary_documents/gvt_reports/USNAVY/tech_rpt_248_45/tech_rpt_248_45_sec6.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>因此，亚铬酸铜又称'''Adkins催化剂'''或'''Lazier催化剂'''。

